Text: Ugh!  This one might have a tiny break in between tunes.  I was rushed by "the wife" to run  errands and I think I uploaded this without checking SBE's.  I'll see if I can re-up it without the SBE's for those who can notice it.
Well, it actually isn't bad.  There isn't the pause break that I thought would be in there.  Sounds fine.  :)
Jerry goes OFF towards the end of Fire On the Mountain!!!  Rare to hear him scream it out like this version does.
